articles.author: Lee Ying Shan
articles.title: Asia-Pacific markets trade mixed as investors parse key regional data - CNBC
articles.description: The Bank of Japan will kickstart its policy meeting Wednesday, and is expected to hold rates when the meeting concludes Thursday.
articles.content:
Asia-Pacific markets traded mixed Wednesday as traders parse a slew of key economic data in the region.
